summary: You need to install Climates of Tamriel and Natural Lighting and Atmospherics for ENB for have the same visual effect like the screens.
descriptionHtml:
THis ENB preset have differents sky color depends where you are in game (the Northen sky don't have the same contrast than the Sothern sky).

You Character need light during the night 'cause you can see something on the dark ;).
